I refuse to take the Trump assassination attempts seriously, as long as conservatives clearly don't take them seriously with their "oooh, it's a direct result of the excessive hysteria whipped up by Harrris and Biden" bullshit. I just love how Harris's message for the final month is "we could be the Republican Party for you, now that the Republican Party is the American Nazi Party".
